name: v4.1.8
body:
**[IrineSistiana/mosdns](https://github.com/IrineSistiana/mosdns/releases/tag/v4.1.8)**
- 修正一个 fast_forward 内存泄漏问题

name: v4.1.6
body:
**[IrineSistiana/mosdns](https://github.com/IrineSistiana/mosdns/releases/tag/v4.1.6)**
- 修正 fast-forward 一个内存泄漏问题
